#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:78
msgid ""
"If [`LIBFOO_VCS_TYPE`](pkg-opt-vcs-type) is configured to `local`, the "
"`--locked` argument is not provided by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:81
msgid ""
"If a package defines build options that define a build profile "
"(`--profile`), the `--release` argument is not provided by default."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:84
#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:117
msgid ""
"The Cargo target directory is based on [`BUILD_DIR`](env-build-dir) and "
"`.releng-tool-cargo-target` folder:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:91
msgid ""
"The environment variable `CARGO_BUILD_JOBS` is populated by either the "
"[`--jobs` argument](arg-jobs), [`LIBFOO_FIXED_JOBS`](pkg-opt-fixed-jobs) "
"or [`LIBFOO_MAX_JOBS`](pkg-opt-max-jobs)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:101
msgid "Install stage"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:104
msgid "The install stage invokes `cargo install` with the arguments:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:124
msgid ""
"The `--root` path will be set to the target sysroot the package should "
"install into (see also [`LIBFOO_INSTALL_TYPE`](pkg-opt-install-type)). "
"`cargo install` may be invoked multiple times for each target it needs to"
" install into. Although, if a package defines build options that define a"
" root path (`--root`), an install is only invoked once with the provided "
"path."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/guides/packages/pkg-type-cargo.md:130
msgid ""
"The installation stage can be skipped by configuring "
"[`LIBFOO_CARGO_NOINSTALL`](pkg-opt-cargo-noinstall)."
msgstr ""

